title: Bobby’s Top 5 Moments From DWTS Premiere + Amy Gets Suspicious Package Sent To Her House + What’s The Haps: Bobby Picks Opry Walk Out Music
itunes:title: Bobby’s Top 5 Moments From DWTS Premiere + Amy Gets Suspicious Package Sent To Her House + What’s The Haps: Bobby Picks Opry Walk Out Music
description:
Bobby picks his top 5 moments after going to the Dancing with the Stars premiere earlier this week and talks about who he met. Amy gets a suspicious package sent to her house and had to call someone to come check it out. We find out what’s going on in our lives during “What The Haps”: Bobby picks his Opry walk-out music, Amy watches Designated Survivor and Lunchbox is getting his foot checked out again.
